{"tid":304351,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣先可以重新愛上一個人","createTime":"2017-06-30T21:02:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T10:46:49.000Z","uid":88385,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca84214559fc7450178ab2c027e53e90cdcf11ea","tid":304351,"uid":88385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T21:02:26.000Z","msg":"我今年20歲 17歲個年同一個大個我兩年既女仔分左手<br />\n佢就好似初戀一樣 好似永遠都忘記唔到<br />\n<br />\n久而久之就由分手單身到宜家 其間唔係無試過去識女仔 但無論同邊個都好似搵唔返個種感覺 因為前女朋友講過唔好再令下一個女仔失望 宜家好似變左陰影咁 好驚一齊左又散 所以一直都唔敢拍拖 又可能因為無拍拖   所以自己好似好懶去經營一段關係（例如比較小主動約朋友食飯）<br />\n<br />\n想問下各位巴絲有咩辦法令自己可以解決呢個現況又或者點樣可以令自己有更大信心去經營一段關係？<br />\n小弟唔識點樣做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個問題已經兩三年 唔想再係咁落去"},{"pid":"69a5f8b0a6ffae8f55b8de571ddf546180b9d316","tid":304351,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T21:03:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比人hurt過就唔會再想拍拖嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n所以放棄把啦"},{"pid":"0f115d05559b2e8d7389eec49d5d156f84a45118","tid":304351,"uid":88385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T21:05:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比人hurt過就唔會再想拍拖嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n所以放棄把啦</blockquote><br />\n有無辦法去解決呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a468c8d5907f5c70eea2bdd2dd297d79133c1a1a","tid":304351,"uid":88385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T21:05:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比人hurt過就唔會再想拍拖嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n所以放棄把啦</blockquote><br />\n有無辦法去解決呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f08272f807c03bfdd42f5ea6c9eb136fd6612609","tid":304